							<ul>
                                    <li>Lot of Hubble data in Optical and UV </li>
                            </ul>
							<li class="fragment"><b>Datacube:</b>
							<ul>
                                    <li>Systematically search for emission:</li>
                                        <ul>
                                                <li>Helium emitters (AM CVn ?) </li>
                                                <li> Planetary Nebula </li>
                                                <li> Active Binaries </li>
                                        </ul>


							</ul>
