                                    <li> Secondary Mass - Period relation: </li>
                                    <ul>
                                    <li> Big error bars mass ratio determination </li>
                                    <li> No TiO and turnoff point: $0.5 \text{ M}_\odot \lesssim \text{M}_{\text{sec}} \lesssim 0.8 \text{ M}_\odot$ </li>
                                    </ul>
                            </ul>
                            <li class="fragment"><b>Outbursts:</b>.
							<ul>
                                    <li>Expected at least one (biased and empirical estimate)</li>
                                    <li> Very rare in globular clusters. Suggests magnetic in nature </li>
							</ul>
							</li>
                            
                            
                            <li class="fragment"><b>Magnetism:</b>
							<ul>
                                    <li> No ionised helium (He II) </li>
                                    <li> Strongest He II outside range (4686 &#8491;) </li>
							</ul>
							</li>
