				<section data-state="sand" data-chapter="Conclusions">
                   <section>
							<h2>Conclusion</h2>
<div class="block">
        An IFU like <em>MUSE</em> can be used to efficiently study the population of compact objects in globular clusters. <em>Deeper observation</em> are needed but a single exposure allowed us to recover the optical spectra of various known X-ray sources. 
						</div>
                    </section>
                </section> <!-- End COnclusion -->
                


